headline: ClearBridge Large Cap Growth Fund Q1 2025 Commentary
summary: The S&P 500 Index declined 4.27% while the benchmark Russell 1000 Growth Index (RLG) fell 9.97%, trailing its value counterpart by over 1,200 basis points.
